N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 203.7 - Research

State Regulations

The commissioner is hereby authorized to contract with any
person or persons, including the New York State College of Agriculture and Life

Sciences, to carry on or cause to be carried on onion production, marketing, storage, product or byproduct research, and to expend any available monies for
such purpose and pursuant to this program. Notes
